{block content}
<body style="background-image: url('/Images/pexels-maria-borisenko-10162332.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: fixed; background-position: center top;">

<div class="position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center bg-light " style="opacity: 0.67">
    <div style="display:flex;align-content: flex-start">
        <input class="btn btn-primary " type="button" value="Back" onclick="history.go(-1)">
    </div>
    <h2 class="display-4 font-weight-normal"> Inspirativni tekst </h2>
    <p class="lead font-weight-normal text-break">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec
        finibus accumsan iaculis. Nam placerat ultricies sem ut interdum. Quisque nec nisi a velit convallis
        varius. Aliquam erat volutpat. Praesent vulputate, nisl sit amet imperdiet sodales, sapien nisi luctus
        ante, ut malesuada felis sapien id nisi. Nulla facilisi. Aenean id felis varius velit cursus ullamcorper
        vel feugiat urna. </p>
</div>
<div style="display: flex;justify-content: center">
    <div  class="position-relative overflow-hidden p-3 p-md-5 m-md-3 text-center bg-light " style="opacity: 0.9;width: 35%; ">
        <table id="secret" class="display">
            <thead>
            <tr>
                <th scope="col">
                    Data from database
                </th>
            </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
            <div n:foreach="$data as $row" class="data">
                <tr>
                    <td>{$row->data}</td>
                </tr>
            </div>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <div n:foreach="$roles as $role">
            <div n:if="$role=='1'">
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <a type="button" class="btn btn-info btn-block" n:href=":Admin:Users:">Admin page</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function() {
        $('#secret').DataTable();
    } );
</script>
</body>
